        <p style="font-family: Montserrat;">Today Ace Airlines is proud to announce and release it's brand new Booking System. This new system will be able to connect to the Ace App, giving you unparalleled access and control over your flights. You will be able to Book flights, Check-In, View flight status, and manage your trips all from the comfort of your computer. "This new advancement in technology will streamline the customers' experience with everything Ace." Drew Crocker claimed. The project began a few months ago as an update to the existing book a flight. However, it quickly became much more than that. This new system will also act as a stepping stone for the electronic boarding passes that will be coming out later this month.</p>

